== Tesalonikarank Pauluchem Dusrem Potr ==
'''Second Epistle to the Thessalonians'''

Tesalonikarank Pauluchem Dusrem Potr zaun asa [[Povitr Pustok|Povitr Pustokant]] [[Novo korar|Novea Koraracho]] ek bhag.


Tesalonikekarance dubav ani bhirant pois krunk aplea poilea potrak titlem ies mellunk na dekhun, Kristachea dusrea ienneachi odil mhaiti ani xikovnn diunk Paulun taktin em dusrem potr boroilem.  Kristachem dusrem iennem lagim pavunk na mhonn Paulu sangta.

Ek vhodd dhormteag vo nastiki (mhonnge Devak ani Tachi Somurt soddun divop) voir sorlea bogor ani Deva-virodhi vo Krista-virodhi dixtti poddlea xivai,  Jezu mhoimen novena ieuncho na mhonn to sangta.  Kristachem disrem iennem lagim pavlam mhonn khatri dhorun, vavr korop nirupeogi mhonn chintun,  kai Tesalonikekaram vaitt jivit jieunk laglolim  :Paulu he chalicher nixed marta ni oslem khotteponn kortoleank Dev khast laitolo mhonn sangta. Zaum tonddim, zaum potr boroun apnnem dil’li xikovnn soglleamnim thiraien samballunk zai mhonn Paulu Tesalonkekarank xiddkaita.

'''Hea Potrachi Manddavoll oxi :''' 

